ed="T" n="0831b02"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0831b02"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000014411"><anchor xml:id="beg0831001"/>天台山<anchor xml:id="end0831001"/></placeName><persName key="A005272">封干師</persName><ptr target="#n2553"/>傳（<persName key="A005272">木𣹟師</persName> <persName key="A004127">寒山子</persName> <persName key="A009211">拾得</persName>）</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0831b03"/><persName key="A005272">釋封干師</persName>者<ptr target="#n2554"/>，本居<placeName key="PL000000014664"><placeName>天台山</placeName><placeName>國清寺</placeName></placeName>也<ptr target="#n546"/>。剪髮齊<lb
ed="T" n="0831b04"/>眉，布裘擁質<ptr target="#n2555"/>，身量可七尺餘。人或借問，止<lb
ed="T" n="0831b05"/>對曰「隨時」二字而已，更無他語<ptr target="#n2556"/>。樂獨舂穀，<lb
ed="T" n="0831b06"/>役同城旦<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1719"/>，應副<ptr type="glossary" target="#g675"/>齋炊。甞乘虎直入松門<ptr target="#n2557"/>──眾<lb
ed="T" n="0831b07"/>僧驚懼──，口唱《唱道歌》<ptr target="#n2558"/>，時眾方皆崇重。及終<lb
ed="T" n="0831b08"/>後，於<date notBefore-iso="+0712-09-16" key="j19813711981836" notAfter-iso="+0713-12-25"><name>先天</name>年中</date>在<placeName key="PL000000042192">京兆</placeName>行化，非恒人之常<lb
ed="T" n="0831b09"/>調，士庶見之，無不傾<anchor xml:id="beg0831sgsz5"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0831sgsz5"/>。以其躡<persName key="A011670">萬迴<roleName>師</roleName></persName>之<lb
ed="T" n="0831b10"/>後，微亦相類，風狂之相過之，言則多中。先<lb
ed="T" n="0831b11"/>是<placeName key="PL000000014664">國清寺</placeName>僧厨中有二苦行曰<persName key="A004127">寒山子</persName>，曰<lb
ed="T" n="0831b12"/><persName key="A009211">拾得</persName>，多於僧厨執爨，爨訖，二人晤語，潛聽<lb
ed="T" n="0831b13"/>者多不體解。亦甚顛狂，糺合相親，蓋同類相<lb
ed="T" n="0831b14"/>求耳。時<persName key="A006334">閭丘<anchor xml:id="beg0831002"/>胤<anchor xml:id="end0831002"/></persName>出牧<placeName key="PL000000014901">丹丘</placeName><ptr target="#n2559"/>，將議巾車<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1720"/>──苦<lb
ed="T" n="0831b15"/>頭疼羌甚，醫工寡効。邂逅<persName key="A005272">干</persName>造，云：「<ref type="person" target="#A005272">某</ref>自<placeName key="PL000000014411">天<lb
ed="T" n="0831b16"/>台</placeName>來謁<ref type="person" target="#A006334">使君</ref>。」且告之患，<persName key="A005272">干</persName>曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A006334">君</ref>何慮乎？」便<lb
ed="T" n="0831b17"/>索淨器，吮水噴之，斯須覺體中頗佳。<persName key="A006334">閭丘</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0831b18"/>異之，乃請<persName key="A005272">干</persName>一言定此行之吉凶。曰：「到任<lb
ed="T" n="0831b19"/>記謁<persName key="A002144">文殊</persName>。」<persName key="A006334">閭丘</persName>曰：「此<ref type="person" target="#A002144">菩薩</ref>何在？」曰：「<placeName key="PL000000014664">國清寺</placeName>厨<lb
ed="T" n="0831b20"/>執爨洗器者是。」<ptr target="#n2560"/>及入<ref type="place" target="#PL000000014664">山寺</ref>，問曰：「<ref type="place" target="#PL000000014664">此寺</ref>曾有<lb
ed="T" n="0831b21"/><persName key="A005272">封干<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>？」曰：「有。」「院在何所？<persName key="A004127">寒山</persName>、<persName key="A009211">拾得</persName>復是何<lb
ed="T" n="0831b22"/>人？」時僧<persName key="A010366">道翹</persName>對曰：「<persName key="A005272">封干</persName>舊院即經藏後，今閴<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g1277"/><lb
ed="T" n="0831b23"/>無人，止有虎豹時來此哮吼耳。<persName key="A004127">寒</persName>、<persName key="A009211">拾</persName>二人<lb
ed="T" n="0831b24"/>見在僧厨執役。」<persName key="A006334">閭丘</persName>入<persName key="A005272">干</persName>房，唯見虎跡縱<lb
ed="T" n="0831b25"/>橫。又問<ptr target="#n2564"/>「<persName key="A005272">干</persName>在此有何行業？」曰：「唯事<anchor xml:id="beg0831sgsz7"/>舂<anchor xml:id="end0831sgsz7"/>穀，供<lb
ed="T" n="0831b26"/>僧粥食，夜則唱歌諷誦不輟。」如是再三<anchor xml:id="beg0831sgsz9"/>歎<anchor xml:id="end0831sgsz9"/><lb
ed="T" n="0831b27"/>嗟。乃入厨。見二人燒柴木，有圍爐之狀。<persName key="A006334">閭<lb
ed="T" n="0831b28"/>丘</persName>拜之，二人連聲咄<anchor xml:id="beg0831003"/>吒<anchor xml:id="end0831003"/>，後執<persName key="A006334">閭丘</persName>手褻之<lb
ed="T" n="0831b29"/>若孾孺，呵呵不已。行<ptr type="glossary" target="#g192"/>曰：「<persName key="A005272">封干</persName>饒舌。<ptr target="#n2561"/>」自此二<pb ed="T" n="0831c" xml:id="T50.2061.0831c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0831c01"/>人相携手出松門，更不復入<ref type="place" target="#PL000000014664">寺</ref>焉<ptr target="#n549"/>。<persName key="A005272">干</persName>又甞<lb
ed="T" n="0831c02"/>入<placeName key="PL000000005250">五臺</placeName>巡<anchor xml:id="beg0831sgsz11"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0831sgsz11"/>，逢一老翁，問曰：「莫是<persName key="A002144">文殊</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0831c03"/>否？」翁曰：「豈可有二<persName key="A002144">文殊</persName>？」<persName key="A005272">干</persName><anchor xml:id="beg0831sgsz13"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0831sgsz13"/>之未起，恍然<lb
ed="T" n="0831c04"/>失之<ptr target="#n2562"/>。</p><p xml:id="pT50p0831c0501"><lb
ed="T" n="0831c05"/>次有<persName key="A012369">木𣹟師</persName>者，多遊<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042189">京邑</ref>市鄽間，亦類<persName key="A005272">封<lb
ed="T" n="0831c06"/>干</persName>，人莫輕測。「封」、「豐」二字，出沒不同<ptr target="#n2569"/>──<persName key="A012370">韋述</persName><anchor xml:id="beg0831004"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>吏</sic><corr>史</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0831004"/><lb
ed="T" n="0831c07"/>官<ptr target="#n2565"/>作「封疆」之「封」，<persName key="A006334">閭丘</persName>序<ptr target="#n2566"/>三賢<ptr target="#n2563"/>作「豐稔」之「豐」，未<lb
ed="T" n="0831c08"/>知孰是。</p><p xml:id="pT50p0831c0901"><lb
ed="T" n="0831c09"/><persName key="A004127">寒山子</persName>者，世謂為貧子風狂之士，弗可恒<lb
ed="T" n="0831c10"/>度推之。隱<placeName key="PL000000014808"><placeName>天台</placeName><placeName>始豐縣</placeName></placeName>西七十里，號為<ref type="place" target="#PL000000014546 #PL000000014558"><name>寒</name>、<lb
ed="T" n="0831c11"/><name>暗</name>二巖</ref><ptr target="#n2568"/>，每於<placeName key="PL000000014546">寒巖</placeName>幽窟中居之，以為定止<ptr target="#n2570"/>。<lb
ed="T" n="0831c12"/>時來<placeName key="PL000000014664">國清寺</placeName>。有<persName key="A009211">拾得</persName>者，寺僧令知食堂<ptr target="#n2567"/>，恒<lb
ed="T" n="0831c13"/>時收拾眾僧殘食菜滓，斷巨竹為筒，投藏<lb
ed="T" n="0831c14"/><anchor xml:id="beg0831sgsz15"/>于<anchor xml:id="end0831sgsz15"/>內。若<persName key="A004127">寒山子</persName>來，即負而去。或廊下徐行，或<lb
ed="T" n="0831c15"/>時叫噪凌人，或望空曼罵。寺僧不耐，以杖<lb
ed="T" n="0831c16"/>逼逐，翻身撫掌，呵呵徐退<ptr target="#n2571"/>。然其布襦零落，面<lb
ed="T" n="0831c17"/>貌枯瘁，以樺皮為冠，曳大木屐。或發辭<lb
ed="T" n="0831c18"/>氣，宛有所歸，歸于佛理。初<persName key="A006334">閭丘</persName>入<ref type="place" target="#PL000000014664">寺</ref>訪問<lb
ed="T" n="0831c19"/><persName key="A004127">寒山</persName>，沙門<persName key="A010366">道翹</persName>對曰：「此人狂病，本居<placeName key="PL000000014546">寒巖</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0831c20"/>間，好吟詞偈，言語不常，或臧或否，終不可<lb
ed="T" n="0831c21"/>知。與寺行者<persName key="A009211">拾得</persName>以為交友，相聚言說，不<lb
ed="T" n="0831c22"/>可詳悉。」寺僧見<ref type="person" target="#A006334">太守</ref>拜之，驚曰：「大官何<anchor xml:id="beg0831sgsz17"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0831sgsz17"/><lb
ed="T" n="0831c23"/>風狂夫耶？」<ref type="person" target="#A009211 #A004127">二人</ref>連臂笑傲出<ref type="place" target="#PL000000014664">寺</ref>。<persName key="A006334">閭丘</persName>復往<lb
ed="T" n="0831c24"/><placeName key="PL000000014546">寒巖</placeName>謁問<ptr target="#n549"/>，并送衣裳藥物，而高聲倡言曰：<lb
ed="T" n="0831c25"/>「賊我賊。<ptr target="#n550"/>」退便身縮入巖石穴縫中，復曰：「報<lb
ed="T" n="0831c26"/>汝諸人，各各努力。」其石穴縫<anchor xml:id="beg0831005"/>泯<anchor xml:id="end0831005"/>然而合，杳<lb
ed="T" n="0831c27"/>無蹤跡。乃令僧<persName key="A010366">道翹</persName>尋<anchor xml:id="beg0831sgsz19"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>共</sic><corr>其</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0831sgsz19"/>遺物，唯於林間<lb
ed="T" n="0831c28"/>綴葉書詞頌并村墅人家屋壁所抄錄，得<lb
ed="T" n="0831c29"/><anchor xml:id="beg0831006"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>二</sic><corr>三</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0831006"/>百餘首<ptr target="#n551"/>，今編成一集，人多諷誦<ptr target="#n2572"/>。後<placeName key="PL000000019959">曹山</placeName><pb ed="T" n="0832a" xml:id="T50.2061.0832a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0832a01"/><persName key="A009449">寂<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>注解，謂之《對寒山子詩》<ptr target="#n1715"/>──以其本無氏<lb
ed="T" n="0832a02"/>族，<placeName key="PL000000013239">越</placeName>民唯呼為<persName key="A004127">寒山子</persName>。至有「庭際何所有，<lb
ed="T" n="0832a03"/>白雲抱幽石」句，歷然<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1721"/>雅體。今巖下有石，亭<lb
ed="T" n="0832a04"/>亭而立，號「幽石」焉。</p><p xml:id="pT50p0832a0501"><lb
ed="T" n="0832a05"/><persName key="A009211">拾得</persName>者，<persName key="A005272">封干禪師</persName>先是偶山行至<placeName key="PL000000014519">赤城</placeName>道側，<lb
ed="T" n="0832a06"/>仍聞兒啼，遂尋之，見一子可數歲<ptr target="#n552"/>已來，初<lb
ed="T" n="0832a07"/>謂牧牛之竪<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1194"/>。委問端倪，云：「無舍，孤棄于此。<ptr target="#n2573"/>」<lb
ed="T" n="0832a08"/><persName key="A005272">封干</persName>携至<placeName key="PL000000014664">國清寺</placeName>，付與典座<ptr type="glossary" target="#g824"/>僧。或人來認，必<lb
ed="T" n="0832a09"/>可還之。後沙門<persName key="A012372">靈熠</persName>攝受之，令知食堂香<lb
ed="T" n="0832a10"/>燈。忽於一日，見其登座，與像對槃而飡。復<lb
ed="T" n="0832a11"/>呼<persName key="A009541">憍陳如</persName>曰「小果聲聞」<ptr target="#n2574"/>。傍若無人，執筯大<lb
ed="T" n="0832a12"/>笑，僧乃驅之。<persName key="A012372">靈熠</persName>咨尊宿<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1722"/>等，罷其堂任，且<lb
ed="T" n="0832a13"/>令厨內滌器，洗濯纔畢，澄濾食滓，以筒盛<lb
ed="T" n="0832a14"/>之。<persName key="A004127">寒山</persName>來，必負而去。又護伽藍神廟，每日僧<lb
ed="T" n="0832a15"/>厨下食，為烏鳥所取狼藉。<persName key="A009211">拾得</persName>以杖扑土<lb
ed="T" n="0832a16"/>偶三二下，罵曰：「汝食不能護，安護伽藍乎？」<lb
ed="T" n="0832a17"/>是夕神附夢與闔寺僧曰：「<persName key="A009211">拾得</persName>打我。」明日<lb
ed="T" n="0832a18"/>諸僧說夢符同，一寺紛然，始知非常人也。時<lb
ed="T" n="0832a19"/>牒申州縣，郡符下云：「賢士隱遁，菩薩應身<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1665"/>，宜<lb
ed="T" n="0832a20"/>用旌之。」號<persName key="A009211">拾得</persName>為賢士<ptr target="#n2575"/>。又於寺莊牧牛，<lb
ed="T" n="0832a21"/>歌詠呼天。當其寺僧布薩<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1291"/>時，<persName key="A009211">拾得</persName>驅牛至<lb
ed="T" n="0832a22"/>僧集堂前，倚門撫掌大笑曰：「悠悠者聚頭。」<lb
ed="T" n="0832a23"/>時持律首座咄曰：「風人何以喧礙說戒？」<persName key="A009211">拾得</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0832a24"/>曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A009211">我</ref>不放牛也，此群牛者多是此寺知僧<lb
ed="T" n="0832a25"/>事人也。」<persName key="A009211">拾得</persName>各呼亡僧法號，牛各應聲而<lb
ed="T" n="0832a26"/>過，舉眾錯愕，咸思改往修來，感菩薩垂跡<lb
ed="T" n="0832a27"/>度脫<ptr target="#n553"/>。時<persName key="A010366">道翹</persName>纂錄<persName key="A004127">寒山</persName>文句於寺土地神廟<lb
ed="T" n="0832a28"/>壁，見<persName key="A009211">拾得</persName>偈詞，附《寒山集》中。</p><p xml:id="pT50p0832a2901"><lb
ed="T" n="0832a29"/>系曰：按<persName key="A005272">封干</persName><date notBefore-iso="+0712-09-16" key="j19813711981836" notAfter-iso="+0713-12-25"><name>先天</name>中</date>遊遨<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042189">京室</ref>，知<persName key="A006334">閭丘</persName>、<persName key="A004127">寒山</persName>、<pb ed="T" n="0832b" xml:id="T50.2061.0832b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0832b01"/><persName key="A009211">拾得</persName>俱<persName key="A002461">睿宗</persName>朝人也，奈何<persName key="A001519">宣<roleName>師</roleName></persName>《高僧傳》中<ptr target="#n554"/>……<persName key="A006334">閭<lb
ed="T" n="0832b02"/>丘</persName>，武臣也<ptr target="#n2577"/>，是<date notBefore-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469511973336" notAfter-iso="+0690-09-16"><name>唐</name>初</date>人。<persName key="A006334">閭丘</persName>序記三人，不言<lb
ed="T" n="0832b03"/>年代，使人悶焉。復賜緋，乃文資也。夫如是，<lb
ed="T" n="0832b04"/>乃有二同姓名<name>閭丘</name>也。又<placeName key="PL000000028694">大溈</placeName><persName key="A001984">祐<roleName>公</roleName></persName>於<persName key="A002120">憲<lb
ed="T" n="0832b05"/>宗</persName>朝遇<persName key="A004127">寒山子</persName>，指其<placeName key="PL000000019708">泐潭</placeName>，仍逢<persName key="A009211">拾得</persName>於<placeName key="PL000000014664">國<lb
ed="T" n="0832b06"/>清</placeName>，知三人是<date notBefore-iso="+0835-03-10" key="j20261062052491" notAfter-iso="+0907-06-06"><name>唐</name>季葉</date>時猶存。夫<persName key="A005272">封干</persName>也，<placeName key="PL000000014411">天台</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0832b07"/>沒而<placeName key="PL000000042192">京兆</placeName>出；<persName key="A004127">寒</persName>、<persName key="A009211">拾</persName>也，<date from-iso="+0712-09-16" key="j19813711981836" to-iso="+0713-12-25"><name>先天</name></date>在而<date from-iso="+0806-01-29" key="j20154742020606" to-iso="+0820-02-17"><name>元和</name></date>逢。為年<lb
ed="T" n="0832b08"/>壽彌長耶？為隱顯不恒耶？《易》象有之，「小狐<lb
ed="T" n="0832b09"/>汔濟」<ptr target="#n2576"/>，其此之謂乎！</p>
